          <p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Lew</placeName><add>&#63;</add>&#58; <date>20 March 1848</date></p>
          <p>My dear Sir&#44;</p>
          <p rend="indent(2)">Enclosed you will receive a ten<lb/> dollar &#40;&#36;10&#41; Bill of the Western Bank of<lb/> <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>&#44; for the Cheap Jewish publi&#45;<lb/>cation society&#95;for the following persons<lb/> <hi rend="underline">towit</hi> <persName role="author">Solomon Cohen</persName>&#44; <persName>Octavius Cohen</persName>&#44; <persName>A. Minis</persName><lb/> <persName>Miss Fanny Y. Cohen</persName>&#44; &#40;<hi rend="underline">care of <persName>Octavius Cohen</persName></hi>&#41; <persName>Isaac<lb/> Cohen</persName>&#44; <persName>M. S. Cohen</persName>&#44; <persName>I. Dela Ilotta</persName>&#44; <persName>Miss<lb/> T. Minis</persName> &#40;care of <persName>A. Minis</persName>&#41; <persName>Miss C. Cohen</persName><lb/> &#40;care of <persName>Solomon Cohen</persName>&#41; &#38; <persName>Theodore Minis</persName><lb/> in all ten. I will try &#38; get you a few<lb/> more&#8212;All of the above are original sub&#45;<lb/>scribers&#44; except the last named&#44; who is a<lb/> new one. Do acknowledge the receipt of<lb/> this &#38; tell me when the year com&#45;<lb/>mences&#44; so that hereafter&#44; I may be<lb/> more regular.</p>
          <p>I wrote you some time since sending<lb/> you ten Dolls&#58; for five Copies of <persName>Miss<lb/> Aguilar&#39;s</persName> Jewish Faith. W<hi rend="underline">as the letter<lb/> received&#63;</hi> I also wrote you a few<lb/> days since a review of <add>&#63;</add> <persName>O&#39;Neal&#39;s</persName><lb/> opinion. I hope it reached you in<lb/> safety. You will now have an<lb/> opportunity of answering my <hi rend="underline">three</hi></p>
    <pb n="2"/>
          <p><hi rend="underline">short</hi> letters. Shorter&#44; than I desire<lb/> them to be&#44; but I am a poor<lb/> correspondent. <persName>Mrs. Cohen</persName> sends<lb/> her kind regards&#8212;truly yours</p>
          <p rend="indent(3)"><hi rend="underline"><persName role="author">Solomon Cohen</persName></hi></p>
		
